title: Tubular Bells collection (gold disk, re-recording, vinyl rip etc
description:
Included are: 
1. The 25th Anniversary version, remastered from the restored master tapes, pressed on a gold disk. 
2. A high quality vinyl rip from a 200g pressing on the Classic Records label, made using a moving coil cartridge and a tube phono stage. 
3. The 2003 re-recording. 
4. The 2009 Ultimate Version, including demo versions. 
5. Orchestral Tubular Bells from 1975
